{{version030}}
{{flavour|Inspires nearby allies of the caster to fight more aggressively, increasing the strength of their blows.}}

'''Battlecry''' is a monster-only spell which briefly gives all nearby allies of the caster the [[might]] [[status effect]], increasing the damage of their blows by 50%. This only affects monsters of the same [[type|genus]] as the caster.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.19]], a caster could only affect allies that had lower [[HD]]. E.g., an [[orc knight]] couldn't buff an [[orc warlord]].
*Battlecry was added in [[0.16]].
